764
01:23:50,400 --> 01:23:53,680
<font color="#ffff00">Wie bitte?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">- Ich bin schwanger.</font>

765
01:24:00,280 --> 01:24:03,880
<font color="#ffff00">Schon wieder?</font>
